column6: Each row is numbered by Denjuu ID.
This is the same ordering as other Denjuu species string tables.
Japanese strings are limited to 16 characters, English is 32 characters.
Some lines stay the same after a Denjuu evolves, and some change.
Repeats within each Denjuu line are labelled in the Notes column.
